movie.title: Hanuman the Immortal 2
movie.description_intro: The thrilling story of Hanuman's adventures with his disciples and a little girl Bindi, who accidentally falls into the forest of Vanars, Vanarvan. Vanarvan is under attack by the demon warrior Rakasur, thousands of years after the war of Lanka. Watch the brave hearts fight for their land and their loved ones against the dark forces.

movies.title: Rock & Rule
movies.summary: Angel, a member of a punk rock band in the apocalyptic future, is kidnapped by Mok, a legendary superocker. Obsessed with a dark experiment, Mok plans to use Angel's voice to summon a demon from another dimension. The rest of the band follows Mok to Nuke York in an attempt to get her back.

movies.title: Ultramarines: A Warhammer 40,000 Movie
movies.summary: A squad of Ultramarines answer a distress call from an Imperial Shrine World. A full Company of Imperial Fists was stationed there, but there is no answer from them. The squad investigates to find out what has happened there.

movies.title: Lucky and Zorba
movies.summary: A dying seagull entrusts her egg to a cat named Zorba, who promises three things: he won't eat the egg, he'll care for the egg, and he'll teach the baby seagull to fly.
